{"id":232659841,"title":"#分享 輕巧的食物袋","content":"覺得攜帶盒子麻煩，那試試輕巧的食物袋吧～一個拳頭大小，隨身帶著不會有負擔\n\n大概可以裝3-4個麵包\n我還看過有人裝麵線羹😂感覺一定要小心翼翼提，而且還裝了兩份😯😯我通常都拿來裝乾的食物\n很多時候會有嘴饞想吃\n麵包、泡芙、紅豆餅、雞蛋糕等\n拿出我的法寶袋～～\n減少塑膠、紙袋的浪費💕\nhttps://i.imgur.com/x2g9Al8.jpg\n非團購文、非商家\n只是告知有優惠，希望藉由告知低價，會讓更多人願意買，一起響應！\n\n剛好看到有同學在學校臉書社團揪團購，才發現！便宜好多～而且新花色真的很好看\nhttps://i.imgur.com/KC5Agr6.jpg\n\n團主原本還很擔心揪不到，沒想到超過預期人數，提早截團～看到有那麼多人願意加入食物袋的行列好開心(*´꒳`*)\nhttps://i.imgur.com/CAWlkcC.jpg\n大家也可以揪揪看","excerpt":"覺得攜帶盒子麻煩，那試試輕巧的食物袋吧～一個拳頭大小，隨身帶著不會有負擔，大概可以裝3-4個麵包，我還看過有人裝麵線羹感覺一定要小心翼翼提，而且還裝了兩份我通常都拿來裝乾的食物，很多時候會有嘴饞想吃，","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":false,"pinned":false,"forumId":"49eed176-a7ad-492c-b6cf-77733ab633ef","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2019-12-10T09:29:58.355Z","updatedAt":"2019-12-10T09:42:26.847Z","commentCount":9,"likeCount":57,"tags":[],"topics":["環保","愛地球","食物袋","無痕飲食","分享"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":true,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"無痕生活","forumAlias":"ecolife","school":"草食性","department":"kai1229","replyTitle":null,"gender":"F","personaSubscriptable":false,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":57}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/x2g9Al8.jpg"},{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/KC5Agr6.jpg"},{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/CAWlkcC.jpg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"c28b6b7d-b489-490b-b526-1479ec773d40","url":"https://i.imgur.com/x2g9Al8l.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/x2g9Al8l.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/x2g9Al8l.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-12-10T09:29:58.355Z","updatedAt":"2019-12-10T09:42:26.847Z"},{"id":"c28b6b7d-b489-490b-b526-1479ec773d40","url":"https://i.imgur.com/x2g9Al8.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://imgur.com/x2g9Al8","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/x2g9Al8l.jpg","type":"image/imgur","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"creat